Features:

* plugins
** a textile plugin
**** regex pattern based substitutions
**** substitute [[<text>]] as link
**** substitute http://xxxx or https://xxxx as link
** 2 columns layout element plugin
** image plugin
*** drag&drop image onto panel
** chart plugin
** table plugin

Bugs or problems need to be improved:

* BUG: dragging element may causing scrollbar to show up when drag&drop to reorder items
* BUG: a new todo with Esc should be canceled
* more smooth way to auto increase textarea height
* data-id instead of html id, so that we can show one story item in 2 stories inside one page
